9-12) they're solidly mid-Expert. Per Main Guide's own inline table (Master 7+) they're
already Master tier. Same party, same AP, two different answers.

--- FINDING 3: TWO FULL MONSTER STAT TABLES DISAGREE EVEN WHERE LABELS MATCH ---
Main Guide Master/TL1: 18/16/14/8, HP 28-42, dmg 12, DR 6-8.
Reference tables Master/TL1: 18/16/14/8, HP 80, dmg 16, DR 8.
